description: Pony Group Inc. provides travel services to individual and group travelers in Guangdong Province and Hong Kong. It offers car services, including carpooling, airport pick-up and drop-off, and personal driver services. The company offers its services through Let's Go, a mobile application that provides multi-language services to international travelers. It serves business companies, travel agencies, or societal associations. The company is based in Shenzhen, the People's Republic of China.
